  17 Sep 2014; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> hwdata-gentoo-0.4.ebuild,
  files/0.4-openchrome.patch:
  EAPI bump. Clean up patch.

  01 Feb 2013; Guy Martin <gmsoft@gentoo.org> hwdata-gentoo-0.4.ebuild:
  hppa stable

  23 Aug 2008; Doug Goldstein <cardoe@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  add GLEP 56 USE flag desc from use.local.desc

  31 Jul 2008; Chris Gianelloni <wolf31o2@gentoo.org>
  hwdata-gentoo-0.4.ebuild:
  Change SRC_URI to point to wolf31o2.org instead of my dev space on
  dev.gentoo.org, since I'm retiring from Gentoo.

  05 Jun 2008; Chris Gianelloni <wolf31o2@gentoo.org>
  -files/0.3-fglrx.patch, -files/0.3-nv-fbdev.patch,
  -files/0.3-nv-vesa.patch, -files/0.3-nvidia.patch,
  -hwdata-gentoo-0.3.ebuild:
  Removing 0.3 version.

  10 Apr 2008; Chris Gianelloni <wolf31o2@gentoo.org>
  +files/0.4-openchrome.patch, hwdata-gentoo-0.4.ebuild:
  Added openchrome patch.

*hwdata-gentoo-0.4 (10 Apr 2008)

  10 Apr 2008; Chris Gianelloni <wolf31o2@gentoo.org>
  +hwdata-gentoo-0.4.ebuild:
  Version bump with some updated information for newer video cards.

  05 Sep 2006; Donnie Berkholz <dberkholz@gentoo.org>;
  hwdata-gentoo-0.3.ebuild:
  Add blocker on hwdata-redhat.

  01 Sep 2006; Chris Gianelloni <wolf31o2@gentoo.org>
  +files/0.3-nv-fbdev.patch, +files/0.3-nv-vesa.patch,
  hwdata-gentoo-0.3.ebuild:
  Added patches from the 2006.1 release to replace the nv driver with either
  vesa or fbdev.

  28 Jun 2006; Chris Gianelloni <wolf31o2@gentoo.org>
  hwdata-gentoo-0.3.ebuild:
  Changed livecd USE flag to binary-drivers USE flag. This will keep us from
  requiring the binary drivers on the LiveCD unless we expressly request it.

  09 Jun 2006; Chris Gianelloni <wolf31o2@gentoo.org>
  -files/0.2-fglrx.patch, -files/0.2-nvidia.patch,
  -hwdata-gentoo-0.2.ebuild:
  Cleaning up older ebuilds.

*hwdata-gentoo-0.3 (23 May 2006)

